Lightroom 5 is working perfectly!

Ran the keygen on a fireproof test box running off of a cd (no hard drive), and the program accepted the number and installed without a hitch.

Adobe had already been blocked for "other reasons" in my hosts file, but I turned off the internet prior to doing the install anyway. Internet is back up, and several start/stop/start cycles of the program reveal no glitches or other issues.

Looks like we're in business.

High praise to Drarbg!
